snippet.title: Fort Boyard | Launch Trailer UK | Microids & Appeal
snippet.description:
The game Fort Boyard will be available as a digital standard edition, on PlayStation 4, Xbox One, Nintendo Switch and PC/Mac June 27th, 2019.

It will be available in physical format, on PlayStation 4 and Nintendo Switch June 27th, 2019 and on Xbox One version July 2nd, 2019.

▪ Instagram : https://www.instagram.com/microids_official/
▪ Facebook : https://www.facebook.com/microids/
▪ Twitter : https://twitter.com/Microids_off
